  "prompt": "If I delete my Tinder account and uninstall the app, does my profile still show to those I've matched with?",
  "response": "If you delete your Tinder account and uninstall the app, your profile will no longer be visible to other users, including those you've matched with. Once you delete your account, all your matches and messages will be removed as well. However, it may take some time for Tinder's servers to fully process the deletion, so there might be a brief period where your profile could still be visible. To ensure your profile is completely removed, it's best to delete your account within the app before uninstalling it.",
